What you need to know:

The underdogs had no choice but to chase an equaliser if they wanted to finish second in the group, but they were caught out again nine minutes from time.De Bruyne's clever pass into the area found Lukaku, who turned and slammed home a right-footed shot to score his 63rd international goal.Finland now face a nervy wait to see if they have done enough, but would need a remarkable run of results to progress.